25E4%25BF%25AE%25E7%25BE%2585.jpg&h=d24316b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拳願競技是日本大型企業之間的鬥爭，商人們賭上巨額利益雇用鬥技者並令其對打之空手格鬥競技。原為平息商人鬥爭之手段，始於江戶中期，並傳承至現代。乃木集團慶安二年創業，以乃木英樹為中心的企業集團、發展運輸業、出版業等業種，是拳願會最古老企業之一。拳願絕命淘汰賽以賭上會長之位所舉辦的格鬥淘汰賽，其舉辦條件是必須獲得五十位會員的贊成..<br />\n<br />\n5 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=d104add3\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=673dd76e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a789c927f5e5db25c5943f498f75532505a64e","tid":1694703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0773e7fcaf43f086edacba1ceaf023456d0d45","tid":1694703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0f5dfd5cd85ff19eda8ab3cbadcb9158d38d72","tid":1694703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"